query:
INSERT INTO liquidity (
                        transaction_version,
                        event_index,
                        block,
                        timestamp,
                        codepoints,
                        nonce,
                        sender,
                        base_amount,
                        quote_amount,
                        lp_coin_amount,
                        base_donation_claim_amount,
                        quote_donation_claim_amount,
                        liquidity_provided
                    )
                    SELECT $1, $2, $3, $4, (SELECT codepoints FROM market WHERE market_id = $5), $6, $7, $8, $9, $10, $11, $12, $13
